OL,6,F"I've always wanted to drive a bus, I
OL,7,Flove meeting new people. I've always
OL,8,Fhad a customer service job but this in
OL,9,Fparticular meant I could drive and see
OL,10,Fpeople," said Jamie.
OL,12,F"I love chatting to people which is
OL,13,Fbrilliant and not much you can do in.
OL,14,Fother jobs, you only get to see them
OL,15,Ffor a short time, but here you get to
OL,16,Fsee them for most of the journey."
OL,18,FWith a first in creative media,
OL,19,FJamie's used his degree from
OL,20,FPortsmouth University
